# Demand Intelligence Platform Architecture

The forecasting system operates across five layers:

1. Data Sources – ingest demand signals from multiple operational systems.
2. Signal Processing – transform raw data into forecasting features.
3. Forecasting Engine – generate SKU-level demand forecasts.
4. Forecast Consumption – power inventory, purchasing and supply planning decisions.
5. Monitoring & Feedback – track forecast accuracy and improve models continuously.


